        public boolean checkContinentDuplicacy()
        Validates the continents and country objects for duplicate values. Traversed adjacent countries and verified all countries are linked.
        Returns:
        true is no duplicates found and if all countries are connected. false for duplicate occurrence and if any country is isolated
